node.text:
#Business101 in 3 short mins with @thealbertpreciado
-
How to turn your idea(s) into reality.. Series A, B and C.. the tangible and intangible value when creating a brand and launching products, choosing when to raise capital and who to bring on as a partner and WHEN (good money vs bad money), allocating funds appropriately and managing/leveraging relationships which can take you and your brand(s) far beyond over a small injection of money
-
#Limitless #Driven #KnowledgeIsPower #EducationMatters

node.text:
Small clip from an interview I did with my friend @thealbertpreciado this past weekend highlighting bits and pieces of when and how I got started in the crazy world of business.. most don’t know this yet but I was 11 years old when I started my first company in 1996
-
The 🔑 to being able to conquer my goals has been my ability to always stay in a positive state of mind & surround myself with like-minded loyal people! 😏🙌🏽👨🏽‍💻
-
#Limitless #Driven

Limitless Challenge
-
Everybody go follow and connect with a friend of mine Jas @LIMITLESS and show your support as I challenge him to a 6-Week Beach Body Transformation on his 35th birthday!!! That’s right… NO CAKE!!! .
#Limitless #TeamWork
